import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';

const Cardproduct = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Card className="cardspanelcontainerParent"style={{ width: '18rem' }}>

    <Card className="product1containerChildren">

    <Card.Img id="product1card" src={require("../images/produit1.jpg")} alt="affichageproduit"/>
    <Card.Body>
      <Card.Title>Confiserie</Card.Title>
      <Card.Text>
        Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the
        bulk of the card's content.
      </Card.Text>
      <Button variant="primary">Cliquez sur le produit</Button>
    </Card.Body>
    </Card>

    <Card className="product2containerChildren">

    <Card.Img id="product2card" src={require("../images/produit1.jpg")} alt="affichageproduit"/>
    <Card.Body>
      <Card.Title>Canelle</Card.Title>
      <Card.Text>
        Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the
        bulk of the card's content.
      </Card.Text>
      <Button variant="primary">Cliquez sur le produit</Button>
    </Card.Body>
    </Card>


    <Card className="product3containerChildren"> 

    <Card.Img id="product3card" src={require("../images/produit1.jpg")} alt="affichageproduit"/>
    <Card.Body>
      <Card.Title>Canelle</Card.Title>
      <Card.Text>
        Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the
        bulk of the card's content.
      </Card.Text>
      <Button variant="primary">Cliquez sur le produit</Button>
    </Card.Body>
    </Card>
    </Card>
    <Card className="product1containerChildren">

<Card.Img id="product1card" src={require("../images/produit1.jpg")} alt="affichageproduit"/>
<Card.Body>
  <Card.Title>Confiserie</Card.Title>
  <Card.Text>
    Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the
    bulk of the card's content.
  </Card.Text>
  <Button variant="primary">Cliquez sur le produit</Button>
</Card.Body>
</Card>

    
    </>
    );
  };
export default Cardproduct;
